      "Code developed over 5 years. (v7.4)",
    icon: "ph:crosshair-light",
  },
  {
    title: "Ad Tracking Built-In.",
    description:
      "User identity, ad and conversion tracking.",
    icon: "ph:git-branch",
  },
  {
  title: "20+ Layouts.",
  description: "Faster development with pre-made layouts.",
  icon: "carbon:cube",
  },
  {
    title: "30+ Integrations.",
    description:
      "Integrate any NPM package.",
    icon: "ph:package-light",
